<TEI xmlns="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0" xmlns:frus="http://history.state.gov/frus/ns/1.0"><text><body><div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1943-10-25T09:35:00-05:00" frus:doc-dateTime-min="1943-10-25T09:35:00-05:00" n="573" subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d573">
                        <note rend="inline" type="source">891.51A/877: Telegram</note>
                        <head>
                            <hi rend="italic">The Minister in Iran</hi> (<persName type="from"><hi rend="italic">Dreyfus</hi></persName>) <hi rend="italic">to the
                                    <gloss type="to">Secretary of State</gloss>
                            </hi>
                        </head>
                        <opener>
                            <dateline rendition="#right">
                                <placeName>
                                    <hi rend="smallcaps">Tehran</hi></placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1943-10-25T18:00:00+03:25">October
                                    25, 1943—6 p.m.</date>
                                <lb/> [Received October 26—12:54 a.m.]</dateline>
                        </opener>
                        <p>1019. The Medjliss, continuing its current wave of activity yesterday
                            passed following three bills: (1) law authorizing employment of 60
                            Americans (2) bill ratifying the trade agreement (see my last one on
                            trade treaty<note n="59" xml:id="d573fn59">Possibly telegram No. 960,
                                September 27, 10 a.m., not printed.</note>) and (3) bill authorizing
                            employment of military mission. I shall now press Foreign Office for
                            signature of Ridley contract. Repeated to Moscow.</p>
                        <closer>
                            <signed>
                                <hi rend="smallcaps">Dreyfus</hi>
                            </signed>
                        </closer>
                    </div>
                    </body></text></TEI>